{"tid":1900142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾南山：疫情不一定發源在中國 4月底基本受控","createTime":"2020-02-27T05:06:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T09:20:49.000Z","uid":172349,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8e0184689c29b81bc47a5bb0b5a143489ac5f0fd","tid":1900142,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T05:06:57.000Z","msg":"新冠病毒疫情不一定發源在中國<br />\n<br />\n鍾南山表示，再過一個階段，中國有可能變成疫情輸入地，所以需要加強國際之間合作，聯防聯控，及時交流掌握到的疫情發展，以及研發有效的治療方法，這樣相信就不會再擴大。他說：「對疫情的預測，我們首先考慮中國，沒考慮國外，現在國外出現一些情況，疫情首先出現在中國，不一定是發源在中國。之前有報道稱華南海鮮市場也許是超級傳播者，但不一定是傳染源！」"},{"pid":"56c9ed6b0b6abb908ed27dbac053b63b2a4df270","tid":1900142,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T05:07:50.000Z","msg":"開始吹風係美國做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote>我地相信，<br />\nYouTube係捍衛香港文化嘅一道防線，<br />\n係光復香港不可或缺嘅一部分。<br />\n<br />\nQ：你地同其他頻道有咩唔同？<br />\nA：此頻道不會盲目洗版叫大家入去CLSS，我地以推廣香港YouTube及捍衛本土文化為宗旨，誠心推薦及介紹不同類型嘅影片，所有影片都係我地精心挑選。<br />\n<br />\n科勞我地：<br />\nYouTube資料庫，收錄超過700個黃藍Channel，持續更新中<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/yellowyoutubehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fyellowyoutubehk&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgaVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=0aebc459\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/yellowyoutubehk</a><br />\nInstagram<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/yellowyoutubehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fyellowyoutubehk%2F&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgaVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=11fac6eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/yellowyoutubehk/</a><br />\nChannel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkyoutubelibrary/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkyoutubelibrary%2F&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgaVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=78ef7511\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkyoutubelibrary/</a><br />\n</blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"891945a6e58895a576eb1274f21f184411241c83","tid":190014